\id PHM - East Kewa NT [kjs] -Papua New Guinea 2004 (web version -2013 bd) 
\h Filemon 
\toc1 Filemon 
\toc2 Filemon 
\toc3 Flm 
\mt1 Filemon  
\imt1 Ripili Agale  
\ip Filemon-re ora adaa ali piruma mo Kolosi su-para Kristen pirisa. Onesimus-ri nipuna kogono naaki pirisa. Nipuna kogono surube ali giyoma pa su meda-para pogola pisa. Go adare-para Onesimus nipu Pol ada muma Kristen-rupa pirisa.  
\ip Go yapi di-ainare Pol nipu karapo ada-para pirisa-pulu Filemon adola pope-rupa marisa. Pare nipumi pepa luma Onesimus kalisa. Go puma Onesimus wala nipuna surube ali piri-para maa rapasa. Go pepa madaare Pol-me Filemon go-rupa lakalisa: Nena kogono naaki rono napagaape lisa. Abiri go kogono naakiri Kristen pia-le Filemon nemere ora nena ame-rupa meape.  
\iot Robonu go-rupa adamina:  
\io1 Filemon epe-rupa aawape agale (1-3)  
\io1 Pol-me Onesimus madaa Filemon agale lakalisa (4-22)  
\io1 Abi awape agale-para beten lae-rupa (23-25)  
\c 1  
\s1 Pol-me Filemon piri pepa luma rapasa  
\p
\v 1 Ni Pol-re Yesu Keriso-na kogono madaa karapo ada-para pi. Naana ame Timoti saa laapome go pepa Filemon pia re-para rapaalepa. Nere ora ni raapu kogono komea-rupa pepa.  
\v 2 Naana bali Apia su-para naana kogono yago ali Akipus-para go pepa rapaalepa. Go page nena ada-para lotu kiritalo pimi enaalinu-para page go pepa rapaalepa.   
\p
\v 3 Naana aapa Gote-para naana Mudu Ali Yesu Keriso laapome nipuna epe raba meape agale-para kuma pi kone-para nimina pu robaa-para maa gina.   
\s1 Filemon-me Mudu Ali kone rulasa  
\p
\v 4 Naa ame Filemon nere ade abuna neme beten to rabu nena bi loma Gote-para ora pili loaayo.  
\v 5 Gore nemere Gote-na ruru enaali madaa ranaame komoma Mudu Ali Yesu madaa kone waru rulaaye-daa remaa pago aayo.  
\v 6 Gore naa nimi kone rulaeme enaalinu raapu kone komea-rupa samina. Go puma naa Yesu raapu piruma nipuna puri raayo adaminalo beten loaayo.  
\v 7 Gore epe ame ali waru paga. Nena ranaa komape konere ora epelea konemere naa lo robaa-para raana komape kone masaaoma puri ora mapalaaya. Gore neme kone go-rupa suaaye rabu Gote-na ruru enaalinuna lo robaa-para epe kone masaaye.   
\s1 Filemon-me Onesimus-ri nipuna ame-rupa lamu misa  
\p
\v 8 Go puma saa Keriso-na ame pipa-pulu neme ele meda paina kone wi. Go puma neme go konere agale mana-rupa lagialo.  
\v 9 Neme ne madaa raana komalo-le neme agale pawa meape. Gore ni Yesu Keriso-na agale lakale ali ya-pulu ni karapo ada-para pi. Go pea puri pale agale nalagialua.  
\v 10 Dia, pare neme Keriso-na pora pamuae kone wisa-daa Onesimus\f + \fr 1.10 \ft Onesimus-ri Filemon-na kogonome adili ali yapare nipu pogola puma Pol raapu pisa. Go pumare nipu Kristen ali-rupa puma pirisa. Juda enaalina rekena agalere go-rupa lea: Kogonome adili ali medaa gupa pogola palia-daare surube alimi yada pi alinu lakeloma repena polopea madaa nilimi tyala pisimi.\f* madaa agale tepa kone wi. Neme karapo piruma neme nipu naa si-rupa kone rulape kone mogeaaya-pulu niri Keriso-na aapa pi.  
\v 11 Abalade nipumiri ne raapu piruma epe kogono napisa. Go pisade pare abiri nipumi saa laapo raita raba meape kogono pala.   
\p
\v 12 Abi nipu wala ne piri-para maa rapaayo. Go pi rabu nana lo robaa-para kone nipu mada pira palae epalia.  
\v 13 Neme epe agale moge riape kogono madaa karapo ada piruaayo-pulu neme Onesimus ni raapu piruma ni raba mina kone sawa. Go puma nena rado-rupa nipu pirula penalo.  
\v 14 Go pea pare neme go madaa nate-daare gore neme nipu nasaapitua. Dia, pare nena koneme nipu epenala kone sali-daare neme nipu mada mea rapaalua.   
\p
\v 15 Gore nipumi abalade ne ogeasi giyasade pare abiri wala nipu ade abuna ne raapu pirapaina.  
\v 16 Go pumare abi nipuri pa kogonome adili naaki-rupadaa napia. Dia, pare abiri nipu ora naana Keriso-na ame ya-pulu nipu madaa pa kogono adili ali pia-daa nalema. Gore neme page nipu ora nana ame ya-pulu raaname komalo. Go pea-le neme nipu mealiri nipu kogono adili naaki epe-rupa piralia. Go pea pare nipu Mudu Ali raapu piruma ora nena ame ya-pulu neme nipu madaa raana ora waru komape.   
\p
\v 17 Go puma neme saa Keriso-na kogono komea pepa kone sali-daare gore ni mulalo agale lage-rupa Onesimus page go-rupa waru mogeaoma meape.  
\v 18 Go pea pare nipumi abalade ne madaa koeyae meda palo pisa-daare ni madaa yago abuto. Go puma nipumi rudu meda mealo pisa-daare gore ni madaa yago abuto.  
\v 19 Niri Pol go agalere ora nana kimi talo: Go ruduri nana abutua. Gore ora nena epe-rupa pirape kone madaare nere ni madaa yago wia-le ake paa-daa neme go madaa agale lano ya?  
\v 20 Gore nina ame Mudu Ali-na bi madaare go epe raana pi kogono pape. Ne saa laapore Keriso-na ame laapo pipa-le go kone madaare neme naa lo robaa-para epe kone masaape.   
\p
\v 21 Neme go pepa epenalalore go agale raluma piraina kone suma pi. Gore neme mo pape talo elenu raayo-para medaloma page mada pali kone salo.  
\v 22 Go pea pare ne agale meda pa lagialo: Neme nina ada pada meda yarare pape. Gore neme kone salo pare Gote-me nimina beten pagalia rabu niri wala nimi raapu madaa mapiraalia kone salo.   
\s1 Agale medaloma lakalisa  
\p
\v 23 Epafras-re ni raapu Yesu Keriso-na kogono madaa karapo ada-para piruaaepa. Go alimiri ne epe-rupa pirape lo agale lo rapaata.  
\v 24 Naa kogono komea-para pi alinu Mak-para Aristarkus-para Demas-para Luk-para nimumi page ne-para epe-rupa pirape lo agale lo rapaateme.   
\p
\v 25 Abiri Mudu Ali Yesu Keriso-me nipuna raba meape kone kuma pi nimina lo robaa-para maa rapaaina. Go puma nimi raapu wina.  
\p Go mada. Ni Pol yaade.   